The Plastic Recycling Show India 2024 showcased the latest innovations and technologies in plastic recycling, featuring advancements in sorting, processing, and reprocessing of plastic waste. Industry experts and stakeholders convened to discuss sustainability challenges and opportunities in India's plastic recycling sector, emphasizing the importance of circular economy principles and environmental stewardship. The event also provided a platform for networking, collaboration, and knowledge exchange among key players in the plastic recycling industry.
